Privacy Policy for Daily Hadiths App

At Daily Hadiths, we respect and value the privacy of our users. We do not collect any personal information from our users, and we do not share any information with third parties.

We do not use any tracking or analytics tools, and we do not display any ads in our app. We only provide daily hadiths for our users to read and enjoy.

Data Sharing and Security:

Since we do not collect any personal information from our users, there is no data sharing or security concern.

Updates to Our Privacy Policy:

If we decide to change our Privacy Policy in the future, we will update this page.

Contact Us:

If you have any questions or concerns regarding our app or privacy policy, please contact us at mustafa@altinisik.net
